190
00:15:09,857 --> 00:15:12,618
So when we get to the last layer where we're actually saying,

191
00:15:13,238 --> 00:15:17,040
what is hurtful behavior towards another user,

192
00:15:17,661 --> 00:15:19,922
the AI model that was fine-tuned to Star Stable

